{"tid":1852704,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"藉兜售口罩詐騙個人資料　澳門政府提醒市民小心","createTime":"2020-01-30T14:33:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T14:33:22.000Z","uid":226984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3c6a85f997d74e8968ab560548da41e875ff12fc","tid":1852704,"uid":226984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T14:33:22.000Z","msg":"澳門衛生局表示，發現有人利用微信，兜售政府提供的口罩，要求居民或持有藍卡的外地僱員傳送身份資料。衛生局長李展潤話，當中存在詐騙成份，市民切勿輕信。<br />\n<br />\n他強調，受保障可以買到政府口罩的澳門居民同外地僱員，只能用身份證正本到指定藥房購買。應變協調中心重申，2月2日會有新一輪口罩供應給市民同外地僱員，市民可以憑證件到10間衛生中心同56間協議藥房登記購買，每人每次可買10個口罩，10日後可以再購買。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1505740-20200130.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1505740-20200130.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=kJJ5Rp8RNWWpGPQirZinAzIStCm0mHK7%2Bbmf%2BnNiY0c%3D&h=00a2b94a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1505740-20200130.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=5114e38d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1505740-20200130.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"}]}